# Testing and quality

## Minimum checks
Run relevant commands after edits:
- format
- lint
- typecheck
- unit tests
- Prisma generate/migration validation
- e2e tests when UI flows are implemented

## Test focus
- SRS scheduling
- quiz scoring
- permissions/RBAC
- i18n fallback
- analytics event ingestion/rollups
- media provenance validation

## Ops
- Provide health endpoints: live, ready, version.
- Include setup and troubleshooting in README.
- Document backup/restore for PostgreSQL and object storage.
